@node limitations "Limitations"
@next regi
@prev usage
@{b}
Why Should I Register?@{ub}

CP is limited to about 12 minutes of user time from the moment the first
screen is shown.  You must register to have unlimited use of this software.

CP currently comes with a limited number of tools. Registration will allow
the user access to many more tools.  CP is modular so tools can be written
extremely quickly.  As a result, registered users of CP will be able to use
almost 100 tools eventually.

Only registered users will receive the full HTML documentation which
will include a lot of text and pictures to aid the understanding
and usage of this product.

@{"            REGISTER              " link regi}

@endnode

